- Primordial: Growth and adaptation
- Infernal: Sacrifice mechanics

Located in faction-specific files under `/frontend/src/components/factions/`

### Crisis Events (85/100)
- Event trigger conditions
- Impact calculation
- Countdown mechanics
- Resolution requirements
- Reward distribution
